pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: header-badge
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 24, 160, 20]
    content:
      style: "$badge"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: FITNEXUS AI

  - elementId: page-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 60, 1060, 45]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Автоустановка агентов: <span style="color:$primary;">новый сервер = мониторинг за 5 минут</span></p>

  - elementId: title-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 110, 50, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: agent1-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 135, 560, 125]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: agent1-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 155, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:server"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$primary"

  - elementId: agent1-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 150, 300, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Zabbix Agent 2

  - elementId: agent1-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 180, 475, 65]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Автоустановка через Ansible → авто-регистрация через API</p>
        <p>Шаблоны: Linux, Docker, PostgreSQL, Nginx | PSK/TLS шифрование</p>

  - elementId: agent2-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 135, 580, 125]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: agent2-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [660, 155, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:chart-line"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: agent2-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [710, 150, 350, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: Prometheus Node Exporter

  - elementId: agent2-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [710, 180, 490, 65]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>CPU, RAM, диск, сеть, systemd-сервисы</p>
        <p>File-based service discovery — авто-добавление хостов</p>

  - elementId: agent3-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 280, 560, 125]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$success"

  - elementId: agent3-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [80, 300, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fab:docker"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$success"

  - elementId: agent3-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 295, 300, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "cAdvisor (Docker)"

  - elementId: agent3-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [130, 325, 475, 65]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Метрики контейнеров: CPU, память, сеть, I/O</p>
        <p>Прямая интеграция с Prometheus</p>

  - elementId: agent4-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [640, 280, 580, 125]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$warning"

  - elementId: agent4-icon
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [660, 300, 36, 36]
    iconName: "fas:database"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$warning"

  - elementId: agent4-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [710, 295, 350, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: PostgreSQL Exporter

  - elementId: agent4-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [710, 325, 490, 65]
    content:
      style: "$bodySmall"
      fontSize: 15
      lineHeight: 1.5
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Коннекты, медленные запросы, размер таблиц</p>
        <p>Статус репликации, WAL-архивирование</p>

  - elementId: flow-bg
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 430, 1160, 220]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"

  - elementId: flow-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [82, 445, 500, 30]
    content:
      style: "$sectionTitle"
      fontSize: 20
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><span style="color:$primary;">Terraform</span> → <span style="color:$accent;">Ansible</span> → <span style="color:$success;">Автоагенты</span> → <span style="color:$warning;">Grafana</span></p>

  - elementId: flow-desc
    elementType: text
    bounds: [82, 485, 1116, 145]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      fontSize: 16
      lineHeight: 1.6
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong style="color:$primary;">1. Terraform</strong> создаёт VM в Yandex Cloud → выводит IP и параметры</p>
        <p><strong style="color:$accent;">2. Ansible</strong> подхватывает через динамический inventory → устанавливает Docker, Nginx, агенты</p>
        <p><strong style="color:$success;">3. Zabbix Agent 2</strong> авто-регистрируется через API → привязывает шаблоны</p>
        <p><strong style="color:$warning;">4. Grafana</strong> подхватывает метрики → дашборды готовы к использованию</p>

  - elementId: bottom-accent
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 690, 40, 3]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"

  - elementId: page-num
    elementType: text
    bounds: [1180, 688, 40, 20]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [right, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: "13"